---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const posts = await getCollection('blog');
posts.sort((a, b) => new Date(b.data.pubDate).valueOf() - new Date(a.data.pubDate).valueOf());
---
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>配当＆優待ナビ | 高配当株・株主優待で不労所得を育てる</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="A8tOtO8MGTE81uwVZVGSbnvRT2F583xupmBPJzmTgKc" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <header class="bg-slate-900 text-white shadow-md py-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wider hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">配当＆優待ナビ 💸</a>
        <span class="text-sm text-slate-300 hidden md:inline">高配当株・株主優待で不労所得を育てる</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="flex-grow max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 w-full">
      <div class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-4">「お金に働いてもらう」仕組みを作ろう。</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          高配当ETFや株主優待銘柄の最新動向を毎日チェック。<br class="hidden md:block" />
          「不労所得」を増やし、経済的なゆとりを作るためのヒントをお届けします。
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-6">最新のレポート</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {posts.map((post) => (
          <a href={`/blog/${post.slug}`} class="block bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-blue-400 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 p-6">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-bold mb-2">{new Date(post.data.pubDate).toLocaleDateString('ja-JP')}</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 leading-tight">{post.data.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm line-clamp-3 mb-4">{post.data.description}</p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold">
              記事を読む <span class="ml-1">→</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 text-center py-6 mt-auto">
      <p class="text-sm">&copy; 2026 配当＆優待ナビ. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
